{"tid":669472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國企業 AT&M 成功收購德國飛機碳纖維零件商 Cotesa","createTime":"2018-05-18T12:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T01:44:14.000Z","uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbd81856e5292b093249f00629f1e2085b22385","tid":669472,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"單嘢早幾星期已經有中國媒體吹風話成咗，已經外媒仲於都報啦~<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">China's AT&amp;M seals takeover of German aerospace supplier Cotesa: Handelsblatt</span><br />\n<br />\nFRANKFURT (Reuters) - China&rsquo;s Advanced Technology &amp; Materials (AT&amp;M) (000969.SZ) has completed its takeover of Cotesa, the head of the German aerospace supplier told the Handelsblatt newspaper, following an investigation by German authorities.<br />\n<br />\nThe German economy ministry in December launched a review of the deal after tightening its rules on foreign corporate takeovers, concerned that important technology and know-how was being transferred to foreign countries.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The deal is done,&rdquo; Cotesa Chief Executive Joerg Huesken was quoted as saying by the paper, which added Berlin had recently approved the transaction.<br />\n<br />\nAT&amp;M counts China Iron &amp; Steel Research Institute as its largest shareholder, a state-owned company that aims to make Chinese aircraft maker Comac competitive with Airbus (AIR.PA) and Boeing (BA.N).<br />\n<br />\n路透社原 link：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-cotesa-m-a-at-m/chinas-atm-seals-takeover-of-german-aerospace-supplier-cotesa-handelsblatt-idUSKCN1II2IS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-cotesa-m-a-at-m%2Fchinas-atm-seals-takeover-of-german-aerospace-supplier-cotesa-handelsblatt-idUSKCN1II2IS&d=V6JraWaE4za4%2B6keL3aCfE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c1345be7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-cotesa-m-a-at-m%2Fchinas-atm-seals-takeover-of-german-aerospace-supplier-cotesa-handelsblatt-idUSKCN1II2IS&h=8dfa572a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-cotesa-m-a-at-m/chinas-atm-seals-takeover-of-german-aerospace-supplier-cotesa-handelsblatt-idUSKCN1II2IS</a><br />\n<br />\nDer Spiegel 嘅 link：<a href=\"http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/unternehmen/airbus-zulieferer-chinesischer-investor-uebernimmt-cotesa-a-1208488.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Fwirtschaft%2Funternehmen%2Fairbus-zulieferer-chinesischer-investor-uebernimmt-cotesa-a-1208488.html&d=V6JraWaE4za4%2B6keL3aCfE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9abe78aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/unternehmen/airbus-zulieferer-chinesischer-investor-uebernimmt-cotesa-a-1208488.html</a>"},{"pid":"d336969f9a6a4971d89ace344729800d54a20435","tid":669472,"uid":45332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"德國燒壞腦？"},{"pid":"c2bb86e112a454de777e77ad20c22e7ae90703b7","tid":669472,"uid":41509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"歐洲國家遲早同中共攬住一齊死"},{"pid":"4d2c4f3161d87463cf93714e8e2e099b43de758b","tid":669472,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:57:35.000Z","msg":"中国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9c9500b2dde92bd631ab77158450e583547b84","tid":669472,"uid":37596,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:58:31.000Z","msg":"搞到歐洲成街恐怖份子又係德國,德國始終係邪惡軸心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e615b7d6112aff05dafa83cf6bcc4232aabf667","tid":669472,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"樓豬用拼音輸入法？"},{"pid":"36c3dcd4319cacbf647e78ee4721b101900875b3","tid":669472,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e615b7d6112aff05dafa83cf6bcc